doc.title: go dira diporokeramo
doc.description: Karolo eno e ka ga go rulaganya

example1.title: {{0}}Sekao sa khoutu ya tsebegae
example1.annotation1: Tlhomamisa gore a ke leina la kgolagano ya dikhomphiutha le le tshwanang Fa go sa nna jalo, busetsa {{0}} mme o se ka wa tlhola o diragatsa.
example1.annotation2: Tlhomamisa gore a ke {{0}} kgotsa tsebegae ya kanale Tsela ya yone e simolola ka letshwao la @ Fa go le jalo, busetsa {{1}}.
example1.annotation3: Tlhomamisa gore a ke tsebe ya vidio Tsela ya yone e simolola ka /watch Fa go le jalo, {{0}} e tla busiwa.
example1.annotation4: Tlhomamisa gore a ke tsebe ya vidio e khutshwane.
example1.annotation5: Mo maemong a mangwe, {{0}} e a busiwa.
